Episode 1 Abby To The Rescue
Abby heads to Warwick, RI to help a struggling dance studio, but finds that the owner is missing and too anxious to even come to her own studio. With dance moms at each others' throats and a building in disrepair, will Abby be able to convince the owner to come back and take control?
